    <scopecontent encodinganalog="520$a">
      <head>Scope and Content
</head>
      <p>Accession 42945: Study documentation records, 1991-2001, include records related to HJR 260 (1994) Study of Juvenile Detention; These records may contain correspondence, articles, briefing materials, legislation, policies, presentation, reports, statistics, summaries, and surveys.  Records have been minimally processed and are in original order.
</p>
    </scopecontent>
